      "content": "hey, i started this 10 day course of antibiotics for a skin infection a few days ago. the redness and swelling are pretty much gone now and i feel 100% better. is it okay if i just stop taking them now so i dont have to deal with the extra side effects? feels like i dont need them anymore if the infection is gone.",
